Package: jpplantnames
Title: Unofficial Japanese Plant Name Lookup Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(
        given = "Kaede",
        family = "Konrai",
        email = "konrai630@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Author: Kaede Konrai
Maintainer: Kaede Konrai <konrai630@gmail.com>
Description: Fetches and caches the Vascular Plant Japanese Name Checklist
    ver. 1.10 and provides helpers for looking up scientific plant names from
    Japanese names. It also includes small optional helpers for checking
    scientific names against the GBIF species match API and WFO Plant List API.
    This package is not affiliated with or endorsed by JBIF, YList, or the
    checklist authors.
